Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 python3,
 python3-pip,
 python3-systemd
Description: small admin CLI for reading systemd journal entries
 simply_journal_admin is a small command-line tool that reads recent systemd journal
 entries through the APT-managed python3-systemd binding. The package ships
 the prebuilt project wheel under /opt/simply_journal_admin and installs it into the
 system Python interpreter via pip during postinst. A systemd unit is
 registered so the CLI can be invoked on demand under journald.
